Question: Tôi muốn tìm các căn nhà ở quận Thanh Trì có hướng Tây Nam
Cypher:
MATCH (:City {name:"bất động sản hà nội"})-[:HAS_LOCATION]->(d:District {name:"thanh trì"})-[:HAS_PROPERTY]->(p:Property)
MATCH (p)-[:HAS_DIRECTION]->(dir:Direction)
WHERE toLower(dir.name) CONTAINS "tây nam"
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_PRICE]->(price:PriceVND)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_AREA]->(area:Area)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_PROPERTY_TYPE]->(ptype:PropertyType)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_LEGAL_STATUS]->(ls:LegalStatus)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_AMENITY]->(amen:Amenity)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_DESIGN]->(design:HouseDesign)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:LOCATED_AT]->(addr:Address)
RETURN DISTINCT
  p.id AS id,
  d.name AS district_name,
  ptype.name AS property_type,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(design.name)) AS house_design,
  toFloat(area.value) AS area_m2,
  toFloat(price.value) AS price_ty_vnd,
  addr.name AS full_address,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(ls.name)) AS legal_status,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(dir.name)) AS direction,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(amen.name)) AS internal_amenities
ORDER BY toFloat(price.value) ASC
LIMIT 10

MATCH (:City {name:"bất động sản hà nội"})-[:HAS_LOCATION]->(d:District {name:"long biên"})-[:HAS_PROPERTY]->(p:Property)
MATCH (p)-[:HAS_DESIGN]->(design:HouseDesign)
MATCH (p)-[:NEAR_FACILITY]->(fac:Facility)
MATCH (p)-[:HAS_PRICE]->(price:PriceVND)
WHERE toLower(design.name) CONTAINS "5 tầng"
  AND toLower(fac.name) CONTAINS "bệnh viện"
  AND toFloat(price.value) >= 4.5 AND toFloat(price.value) <= 5.5
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_PROPERTY_TYPE]->(ptype:PropertyType)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_AREA]->(area:Area)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_LEGAL_STATUS]->(ls:LegalStatus)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_DIRECTION]->(dir:Direction)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_AMENITY]->(amen:Amenity)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:LOCATED_AT]->(addr:Address)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[:HAS_CONTACT]->(c:Contact)
OPTIONAL MATCH (c)-[:HAS_CONTACT_NAME]->(cn:ContactName)
OPTIONAL MATCH (c)-[:HAS_CONTACT_PHONE]->(cp:ContactPhone)
RETURN DISTINCT
  p.id AS id,
  d.name AS district_name,
  ptype.name AS property_type,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(design.name)) AS house_design,
  toFloat(area.value) AS area_m2,
  toFloat(price.value) AS price_ty_vnd,
  addr.name AS full_address,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(ls.name)) AS legal_status,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(dir.name)) AS direction,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(amen.name)) AS internal_amenities,
  COLLECT(DISTINCT toLower(fac.name)) AS near_facilities,
  head(COLLECT(DISTINCT cn.name)) AS contact_name,
  head(COLLECT(DISTINCT cp.number)) AS contact_phone
ORDER BY toFloat(price.value) ASC
LIMIT 10;
